'''''Polyhedron'' 104''' was a roleplaying magazine from [[February]] of [[1995]]. It contained many roleplaying articles, including an adventure for [[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game]]. The article was called "[[Dangers from the Dark Side: Villains for the Star Wars: New Republic Campaign, Part Two]]" and was written by [[Bill Slavicsek]] and [[Michele Carter]].

